   (function getAds() {
            var userAgent = navigator.userAgent || navigator.vendor || window.opera;
            var deviceType;
            var mobileID = 770; //Specific to the publisher
            var desktopID = 769; //Specific to the publisher
            var networkID = 156230; //Pubmatic network ID
            var breakSize = 768; // Size to categorise whether device is a desktop or mobile
            if ((userAgent.match(/iPad/i) || userAgent.match(/iPhone/i) || userAgent.match(/iPod/i) || userAgent.match(/Android/i)) && window.innerWidth <= breakSize) {
              deviceType = mobileID;
            } else {
              deviceType = desktopID;
            }
            var purl = window.location.href;
            var url = '//ads.pubmatic.com/AdServer/js/pwt/' + networkID + '/' + deviceType;
            var profileVersionId = '';
            if (purl.indexOf('pwtv=') > 0) {
              var regexp = /pwtv=(.*?)(&|$)/g;
              var matches = regexp.exec(purl);
              if (matches.length >= 2 && matches[1].length > 0) {
                profileVersionId = '/' + matches[1];
              }
            }
            var wtads = document.createElement('script');
            wtads.async = true;
            wtads.type = 'text/javascript';
            wtads.src = url + profileVersionId + '/pwt.js';
            var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
            node.parentNode.insertBefore(wtads, node);
           })();
  </script>

    }
    var args = _extends({}, params, {
        hostname: navigate.hostname,
        url: url,
        path: path,
        pageNo: query.pageNo
    });
    return _page2.default.read(args).then(function (content) {
        if (content instanceof Error) context.dispatch('LOAD_CONTENT_FAILED', content);else context.dispatch('LOAD_CONTENT', _extends({}, content, { request: { payload: payload } }));
    }, function (error) {
        return context.dispatch('LOAD_CONTENT_FAILED', error);
    });
